com.interpss.simu.multicase.result
Interface AclfBusResultRec

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfBusResultRecImpl
public interface AclfBusResultRec
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Aclf Bus Result Rec'. AclfBusResultRec is used for recording the bus result and the bus result summary. voltMsgPU is for bus result. The other fields are for bus summary result. Bus summary result is used for storing summary of multiple study cases, for example, in security margin analysis.

The following features are supported:

  • Volt Mag PU
  • High Volt Mag PU
  • Desc High Voltage
  • Low Volt Mag PU
  • Desc Low Voltage
